{"tid":1630432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【極嚴重】連登正被五毛大軍全面滲透","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:03.000Z","uid":67232,"like":62,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"428607f07b9e9def7cfe84a0bdacb1539293c346","tid":1630432,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"我相信明眼人呢幾日都feel到連登好唔正常，睇住熱門成日都喺到屌嚟屌去。<br />\n<br />\n例如嘈埋D幫唔幫人裝修<br />\n有一班人就話:唔好裝修呀，失民心呀，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再用任何方法搞其他店舖</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就會有人屌:而家係咪乜撚都唔搞得先?有班人甚至吹風見藍就裝修<br />\n<br />\n之後咁撚樣互屌就屌撚咗一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有人提出黑裝修紅裝飾呢D吸納咗兩邊意見，嗰班友係唔撚會理架，繼續屌到永無止境。<br />\n<br />\n仲有人吹風要燒法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家出面熱門就嘈撚住話道唔道歉，掟火係鬼。共產黨對付群眾運動永遠都係用呢個方法:先分化，令我哋內耗，再重點擊破勇武，後解決人數佔百幾萬嘅和理非，呢場運動就可以收皮。<br />\n<br />\n連登一直都有五毛長期用呢招互屌，但我見呢幾日嘅分裂係特別嚴重，睇嚟共產黨十一之後維穩落多咗唔少功夫。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁有咩解決方法呢</span></span>?<br />\n<br />\n咁多位，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係搓下你哋個心啦</span></span>，我哋出嚟係做緊乜呀，個目標係咩呀?爭取自由民主，點實現呀?<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家最重要嘅戰線係國際戰線</span></span>唔係問要唔要做裝修佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋而家最強最有力嘅武器就係人權法，通過人權法要得到美國人民甚至國際支持，所以我哋要企喺道德高地爭取支持。<br />\n<br />\n呢排居然有人吹風話打仗唔使講道德，搬埋毛澤東出嚟講。毛澤東拉攏對象係農民，所以佢玩鬥地主，咁我哋拉攏美國係咪要做道德撚先?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">停止分化集中對付三大敵人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">港共政府</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">香港警察</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"a5f68a5262d4b71af6fda145724763a8bfa04eed","tid":1630432,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2f929cb279c908c6a0b54bb81786d0514e2ef1f","tid":1630432,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"負皮嘅入嚟屌柒我囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb8125183e1128051e291f9ac625c9eed3196f0","tid":1630432,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb04c25f469ca9a15cbaa30655c6ea73de91e58b","tid":1630432,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:35:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a830b4620578022790c262936b026799f88c2eb4","tid":1630432,"uid":19437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"乖。忍多陣。我都想快d過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b792502cbe8463f22219fda20ed4ff4bb94e187c","tid":1630432,"uid":120541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:00.000Z","msg":"和理非呢個時候係全力文宣貼連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n勇武咁辛苦係出面打生打死，用生命去換來挨槍畫面、止暴制共、斷共米路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喂，我地香港人有割蓆、互屌、退路揀咩？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家醒下啦"},{"pid":"3e6bc55a3e2597abd3d097b067fa016cccc58af2","tid":1630432,"uid":326076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:38:37.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"f9943080cceb7f282276cdbfc2d575524910119a","tid":1630432,"uid":128963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:38:51.000Z","msg":"啱，對準真正的敵人ccp"},{"pid":"166ce574bb4af693dc26af1c7a11f0ad2f51cf09","tid":1630432,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a9534df8c2768d8b7338c856296e1840e886bb4","tid":1630432,"uid":71306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好比人分化啊"},{"pid":"0de3b87e10daf5fd24e93cc13ad03df0489419a5","tid":1630432,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a9534df8c2768d8b7338c856296e1840e886bb4","tid":1630432,"uid":71306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好比人分化啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:53.000Z","msg":"真係六月至今最嚴重嘅一次"},{"pid":"280b383fcb8d5b9f3481a6edb740c76e17744e49","tid":1630432,"uid":254596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:48.000Z","msg":"我求哂吓你哋保持冷靜"},{"pid":"d161ce8e6c2750221da6d3e6a0a9fb7d39ecbfd0","tid":1630432,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"280b383fcb8d5b9f3481a6edb740c76e17744e49","tid":1630432,"uid":254596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:48.000Z","msg":"我求哂吓你哋保持冷靜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:42:10.000Z","msg":"初心"},{"pid":"b2be702bb33617981b6ff6ca5c6ccdbb0ccaed72","tid":1630432,"uid":71306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"停止分化集中對付三大敵人<br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨<br />\n港共政府<br />\n香港警察<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"5fb38b4e7180b54db4f95e1b987add49d473cc68","tid":1630432,"uid":13318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"推 不分化 不割蓆 加強對外文宣"},{"pid":"6f3b9f9cb2f3f3ef4f3a508edaff59637765bf19","tid":