:0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"428607f07b9e9def7cfe84a0bdacb1539293c346","tid":1630432,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"我相信明眼人呢幾日都feel到連登好唔正常，睇住熱門成日都喺到屌嚟屌去。<br />\n<br />\n例如嘈埋D幫唔幫人裝修<br />\n有一班人就話:唔好裝修呀，失民心呀，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再用任何方法搞其他店舖</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就會有人屌:而家係咪乜撚都唔搞得先?有班人甚至吹風見藍就裝修<br />\n<br />\n之後咁撚樣互屌就屌撚咗一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有人提出黑裝修紅裝飾呢D吸納咗兩邊意見，嗰班友係唔撚會理架，繼續屌到永無止境。<br />\n<br />\n仲有人吹風要燒法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家出面熱門就嘈撚住話道唔道歉，掟火係鬼。共產黨對付群眾運動永遠都係用呢個方法:先分化，令我哋內耗，再重點擊破勇武，後解決人數佔百幾萬嘅和理非，呢場運動就可以收皮。<br />\n<br />\n連登一直都有五毛長期用呢招互屌，但我見呢幾日嘅分裂係特別嚴重，睇嚟共產黨十一之後維穩落多咗唔少功夫。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁有咩解決方法呢</span></span>?<br />\n<br />\n咁多位，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係搓下你哋個心啦</span></span>，我哋出嚟係做緊乜呀，個目標係咩呀?爭取自由民主，點實現呀?<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家最重要嘅戰線係國際戰線</span></span>唔係問要唔要做裝修佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋而家最強最有力嘅武器就係人權法，通過人權法要得到美國人民甚至國際支持，所以我哋要企喺道德高地爭取支持。<br />\n<br />\n呢排居然有人吹風話打仗唔使講道德，搬埋毛澤東出嚟講。毛澤東拉攏對象係農民，所以佢玩鬥地主，咁我哋拉攏美國係咪要做道德撚先?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">停止分化集中對付三大敵人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">港共政府</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">香港警察</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:49:15.000Z","msg":"對準政權<br />\n<br />\n究竟你地知唔知依場運動要點維持落去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630335</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c92511f51ac5f96904499e41f649d0a32ba8f4c","tid":1630432,"uid":203393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"冷靜D啦！各位唔好互屌！"},{"pid":"2554847bd4e5472d2f61b7efe780f3cdd8ebad5d","tid":1630432,"uid":4510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e23e543b00276b0dcd8c82ae589eb966ba930d52","tid":1630432,"uid":187629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c2aff3593848753d5038d86bc121c68bf5af453","tid":1630432,"uid":4510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e453c6d3ff8fe1f7754ebb33a449d44cf1c9735e","tid":1630432,"uid":71306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"而家最重要嘅戰線係國際戰線唔係做裝修佬！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8017aa8c3a6f3c6fbe741e19543f7b8978646d8","tid":1630432,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:50:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfe3585d926c3818c88683806f4d15e068664c26","tid":1630432,"uid":5588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a38de99d993484df71b82e71d3275a0ecfe6130","tid":1630432,"uid":71306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383975704df6c06513f6137ae5acbeae4d1688cb","tid":1630432,"uid":34584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"465ef0009234042d9a5252fdc8b0ed76d66cba91","tid":1630432,"uid":6